Nodes.Comment: Spam-click interact while running along the pipe to plug the holes.
Finish the Heart here by feeding the animals. The food has a fast respawn.
You can [weapon-swap] open the Bushes and Missed Spots in the Mansion.
Repeat the Hard challenge til you're done (if you can't solo it, continue to the next POI and do the Hard solo challenge near it).
Don't kill any Centaurs on the way to the Heart (wait for the Heart node).
You can [weapon-swap] smash the food. If you're lucky Rock Dogs are up. Kill everything in the path.
Activate all Brawlers at once and AoE them down.

DetachedNodes.Comment: Pop all Spider Eggs. Kill all the Hatchlings but escape the Champion that may spawn.
These can be smashed trough the fence too.
